{"prompt": "Generate a website for a SaaS product. The website should be rustic and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Rustic SaaS</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-blue: #4682B4; /* Steel Blue */\n            --secondary-blue: #87CEEB; /* Sky Blue */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #F5F5DC; /* Beige */\n            --card-background: #FAF0E6; /* Linen */\n            --button-hover-bg: #5A9BD4;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        #header {\n            background: var(--brand-blue);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #333333 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        #header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        #main-section {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #main-section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        #main-section p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto 30px auto;\n        }\n\n        .features {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            width: 30%;\n            min-width: 250px;\n            background-color: var(--card-background);\n            padding: 25px;\n            margin: 15px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--brand-blue);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            margin-bottom: 0;\n        }\n\n        #cta {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--secondary-blue), var(--brand-blue));\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 50px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 -2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        #cta h2 {\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--button-hover-bg);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            border-color: var(--brand-blue);\n        }\n\n        #footer {\n            background-color: #333333;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        #footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            #header h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .feature-item {\n                width: 80%;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header id=\"header\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>RusticFlow</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"main-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Streamline Your Workflow with Rustic Charm</h2>\n            <p>RusticFlow offers a powerful yet simple solution to manage your projects and tasks. Designed with clarity and ease-of-use in mind, it brings a touch of timeless elegance to your digital workspace.</p>\n            <div class=\"features\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Intuitive Design</h3>\n                    <p>Navigate your projects with a clean, user-friendly interface that feels familiar and comforting.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Robust Features</h3>\n                    <p>From task assignment to progress tracking, RusticFlow provides all the tools you need without the clutter.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <h3>Seamless Collaboration</h3>\n                    <p>Work together with your team effortlessly. Share updates, assign tasks, and stay in sync.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"cta\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Ready to Simplify Your Work?</h2>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Start Your Free Trial</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer id=\"footer\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 RusticFlow. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic JavaScript for potential future enhancements\n        document.querySelectorAll('.cta-button').forEach(button => {\n            button.addEventListener('click', function(e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                alert('Redirecting to sign-up page!');\n                // In a real app, you would navigate the user to the sign-up page\n                // window.location.href = '/signup';\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}